.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, fishing, rock-climbing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
3. the fan indie is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the fan pop and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | fishing    | chess | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

