.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, cucumber, grapes
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, trike
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the person eating grapes is not the person driving the bike##6
3. the person driving the bus is the person eating grapes##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person eating grapes##6
6. the person eating blueberry is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | asparagus  | cucumber | blueberry | grapes |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike     | trike     | bus    |

